text: Novy () is a rural locality (a village) in Nadezhdinsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 31 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 52 km from Iglino, 2 km from Pyatiletka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Novy, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
